  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439320/extras/c623087765d7272516a9656de657201a.poster.avif?t=1743491546\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439320/extras/c623087765d7272516a9656de657201a.webm?t=1743491546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439320/extras/c623087765d7272516a9656de657201a.mp4?t=1743491546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Red or Blue? Your choice decides life or death.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You wake up in a strange room, faced with two buttons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the instructions on the screen and press a button.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are no lies, but you must choose wisely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sometimes, a button will change the room. Other times, it will light up one of the five lamps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If all five lamps light up, you survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, not all choices are that simple.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you escape this room?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Red or Blue is a mystery game with horror elements, offering a playtime of approximately 120 minutes.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439320/extras/c623087765d7272516a9656de657201a.poster.avif?t=1743491546\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439320/extras/c623087765d7272516a9656de657201a.webm?t=1743491546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439320/extras/c623087765d7272516a9656de657201a.mp4?t=1743491546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Red or Blue? Your choice decides life or death.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You wake up in a strange room, faced with two buttons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the instructions on the screen and press a button.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are no lies, but you must choose wisely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sometimes, a button will change the room. Other times, it will light up one of the five lamps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If all five lamps light up, you survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, not all choices are that simple.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you escape this room?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Red or Blue is a mystery game with horror elements, offering a playtime of approximately 120 minutes.</p>",
